children.characters:
# template for metric tables

SELECT
  pt,
  ... as object_id,
  ... as metric_variable
FROM `...`
WHERE pt >= TIMESTAMP('{{ start_date }}')
  AND pt <= TIMESTAMP('{{ end_date }}')
  ...
